@host = http://localhost:7071

# Versioning test: start a v1 instance (pauses on wait-for-event inside sub-orch),
# then start a v2 instance alongside it, confirm each independently.
# Sub-orch instance IDs are deterministic: {parentId}:RunSubOrch:primary

### VersionTest v1: Start
POST {{host}}/api/workflows/VersionTest:1
Content-Type: application/json

{ }

###
@vtV1Id = fcb01197a50249f58bfe0d147de54d91

### VersionTest v1: Check status
GET {{host}}/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances/{{vtV1Id}}

### VersionTest v2: Start
POST {{host}}/api/workflows/VersionTest:2
Content-Type: application/json

{ }

###
@vtV2Id = 9f36051949f7478b8573cbb9f15cfd4e

### VersionTest v2: Check status
GET {{host}}/runtime/webhooks/durabletask/instances/{{vtV2Id}}

### VersionTest v1: Confirm sub-orch (logs "VersionTestSubOrch v1" in app logs)
POST {{host}}/api/events/{{vtV1Id}}:RunSubOrch:primary/VersionTestConfirmed
Content-Type: application/json

{ "confirmedBy": "tester" }

### VersionTest v2: Confirm sub-orch (logs "VersionTestSubOrch v2" in app logs)
POST {{host}}/api/events/{{vtV2Id}}:RunSubOrch:primary/VersionTestConfirmed
Content-Type: application/json

{ "confirmedBy": "tester" }
